    <S id="022S1">
        <FORM kindOf="original">aitsu a kadjunangan qinadjayan ni Salakats tua quay katua tsatsuken.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="original">aiʦu a kaɉunaŋan qinaɉajan ni saɭakaʦ tua quaj katua ʦaʦukən.</PHON>
        <FORM kindOf="standard">aicu a kadjunangan qinadjayan ni Salakac tua quay katua cacuken.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="standard">aiʦu a kaɉunaŋan qinaɉajan ni saɣakaʦ tua quaj katua ʦaʦukən.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en">This earth is tied up by Salakats with rattans and vines.</TRANSL>
